## Guidance for Future ChatGPT/Codex Work

When modifying this app:

- Keep UI mobile-first.
- Do not show cost on staff Input screen.
- Keep Google Sheet as source of truth.
- Never push default empty local data to Google Sheet on first load.
- Preserve Nomono visual system.
- Keep staff workflow fast: one session input should take under 30 seconds.
- Use `npm run build` before deploy.
- Push to GitHub `main`, then deploy to Vercel production.
